Question 1
Identify the correct data type for the Product Price column in the following table.

Product ID      Product Price
P1              13.50
P2              22.75



product_price TINYINT


product_price STRING


product_price DECIMAL


product_price INT

Correct
Correct! A decimal should be used as the data type in this column as the price may include a fraction value.

